The Xenoforce shuttle was now in earth orbiter.

Siref:Any sign of his spark?

Rycal:Not yet but I don't scanned ever....wait I got a signal.Its him 
its pegatron!

Siref:Good!Now enter the atmosphere of earth!

Rycal:Starting countdown...5...4...3...2...1...0.........we're now in 
the atmosphere boss!

Siref:Ok then!Go for the location!

Rycal:Roger!

Pegatron was outside the base only to take some rest until he saw the 
shuttle coming."DAMMIT I DIDN'T CONTACT THEM!!!"So when the shuttle 
landed he was just in front of it and the doors opened.

Pegatron:.......Hey guys!

Siref:Where have you been we were searching for you.

Pegatron:Lets say I had some little problems....

Siref:Anyway lets end this conversation and lets go.

Pegatron:Sorry chef but I'm not moving from this planet.

Siref:And why is that so?

Pegatron:There's a war here and they need my help and if you don't 
mind I would like the team to stay here to.

Siref:..........Permission accorded.

The rest of the team get out.

Moren:WAAAAAAAAAAA PEG WHERE THE HELL HAVE YOU BEEN DAMMIT YOU COULD 
AT LEAST CONTACT US I THINKED YOU WERE DEAD!!!!!!

Pegatron:HEY HEY MOREN RELAX I'M NOT DEAD YET AND NOT FOR A LONG TIME 
SO STOP THAT OK?

Lyas:Still think you're invincibel don't you?

Pegatron:And you you're still angry with anyone?

Lyas:WATCH YOUR LANGUAGE!

Rycal:Hey kiddo!So you've made it to here as I see?

Pegatron:Yeah pop and your trick to enter the atmosphere worked!

Rycal:Good to see that I'm not talking for nothing.

Siref:OK PEOPLE WE GOT A WAR TO FINISH SO THE FASTEST WE WIN THE 
FASTEST WE GO HOME HUNDERSTOOD?

Xenoforce:SIR!YES SIR!

Siref:Good you've got a break till next order.
